A4.text: Acmeism emerged c. 1911 or in 1912 in Russia under the leadership of Nikolay Gumilev and Sergei Gorodetsky.

A5.text: The group originally met in The Stray Dog Cafe, St. Petersburg, then a celebrated meeting place for artists and writers.
